{"tid":2159643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通訊事務管理局同消委會走得好前！","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T12:41:14.000Z","uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f38e50f9756571a9d8b44e6366af442de60b5dff","tid":2159643,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"通訊事務管理局<br />\n<br />\n固定期限合約期滿通知<br />\n電訊服務供應商須於合約期滿前不多於六十天及不少於三十天，通知用戶合約即將期滿，或提供合理的方法讓用戶翻查合約到期日；及<br />\n<span class=\"red\">除非用戶特意表明，否則服務供應商不可自動替用戶續約。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ofca.gov.hk/tc/consumer_focus/education_corner/alerts/tsc/cpic/procedures/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ofca.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fconsumer_focus%2Feducation_corner%2Falerts%2Ftsc%2Fcpic%2Fprocedures%2Findex.html&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=daf713e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ofca.gov.hk/tc/consumer_focus/education_corner/alerts/tsc/cpic/procedures/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消費者委員會<br />\n<br />\nK. 自動續約<br />\n很多合約都有訂明在合約期屆滿後，認購的服務將會被自動續期。<br />\n<br />\n如合約內沒有相關條款要求供應商於合約屆滿前的合理時間內，就有關續約後增加收費及服務限制等方面，向消費者發出一個清晰而明確的書面提示，<span class=\"red\">這類條款是不公平的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/competition_issues/reports/20120403.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumer.org.hk%2Fws_chi%2Fcompetition_issues%2Freports%2F20120403.html&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=df30da71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/competition_issues/reports/20120403.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">消委會委員由香港行政長官委任</span>，經費主要來自香港納稅人(from wikipeida)"},{"pid":"1abb1c3cde7daa1a85b8f82b4231367933ef3fdb","tid":2159643,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"咁係咪個客冇主動話續約就可以單方面cut9佢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5b66dce1ff73286fed3dc7661f0f953a9936b5","tid":2159643,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1abb1c3cde7daa1a85b8f82b4231367933ef3fdb","tid":2159643,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"咁係咪個客冇主動話續約就可以單方面cut9佢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"依家係無啦啦話要你續約，續約係比機會你改過自身添呀"}]}